<br>
As has already been stated - if you leave a camp your claim is gone (fighting in the hallway outside a room is not leaving a camp - you are still fighting in a general area and some camps have pull spots or roamers that you can pull to supplement yourself). If you are AFK and the camp is at full spawn, your camp is gone. If you are sitting there preparing to break and someone leapfrogs you, that is rude and I will ask them to move on before I get nasty. KSing is not acceptable in any case. If you see someone in the area, send them a tell asking if they claim the camp. Just taking it is rude. It's also rude to automatically threaten someone and berate them for campstealing and KSing without trying to work out a compromise. <p>Vulrath Vadrigaar<br>
